      "content": "hey so im a student in berlin and things are super stressful right now with finals coming up. im currently on sertraline for my mood but it feels like it's not quite doing enough to help with the anxiety/stress. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine since its natural and might give me a bit of an extra boost. do u think it's okay to take them together or is that a bad idea?",
