      "content": "serotonin syndrome sounds scary but i've read it's pretty rare if you're just taking standard doses. if i just take a small amount of the supplement, like half a pill or something, would that make it okay? i really need this extra help to get through this month and i don't want to deal with a doctor right now. it's just a natural herb, surely it's not going to cause a major medical emergency if i'm careful?",
